Wednesday, January 29, 1997

MERIT DOCKET

96-2585. Coleman v. Ohio Adult Parole Auth.

Franklin App. No. 96APE03-353. On motion to dismiss and on motion for hearing on appellee’s motion to dismiss. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. *1542F.E. Sweeney, J., would grant the motion to dismiss and deny the motion for hearing. Pfeifer, J., would deny the motion to dismiss and deny the motion for hearing.
